# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>Federated Suns infantry benefit from one of the strongest industrial bases in the Inner Sphere, with AFFS quartermasters able to supply platoons with standardized equipment and ammunition from a logistics network that few rival states can match. Towing Thumper cannon, a direct-fire variant of the standard Thumper artillery tube, these platoons deliver heavy shell fire against visible targets without the arc trajectory of indirect systems.</p>
</overview>

